hotspot.title: Security precautions
hotspot.description: Security precautions in a cold storage warehouse include controlled access, surveillance systems, personnel authentication, temperature monitoring, and inventory tracking to safeguard temperature-sensitive goods from theft, tampering, and unauthorized access.

hotspot.title: Safe Workloading
hotspot.description: The safe workloading process involves assessing and optimizing the weight and distribution of loads, utilizing proper equipment, and adhering to safety guidelines to prevent injuries and ensure a secure working environment.

hotspot.title: Watch loading process
